                <head>Revival of Know Nothingism</head>
                <origin>Georgia Exchange</origin>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p>"We overheard a few days ago the following interesting and important
                        conversation between two 'culled pussons' of a complexion somewhere between
                        that of an ace of spades and the outside of a black kettle, who were
                        leisurely sunning themselves up on a wood pile."</p>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Mocks a conversation between two blacks supposedly lamenting the
                    importation of blacks to America.</summary>
                <note>aubrowser/rvmar59.html#3.26a</note>
